metadata.description: SHA-1 is a weak hash known to have hash collisions.

App can read/write to External Storage. Any App can read data written to External Storage.
App creates temp file. Sensitive information should never be written into a temp file.
This App copies data to clipboard. Sensitive data should not be copied to clipboard as other applications can access it.
This app has capabilities to prevent tapjacking attacks.
App uses SQLite Database and execute raw SQL query. Untrusted user input in raw SQL queries can cause SQL Injection. Also sensitive information should be encrypted and written to the database.

metadata.description: This App may have root detection capabilities.

metadata.cwe: CWE-780 - Use of RSA Algorithm without OAEP

playstore_details.title: Coinhako: Buy Bitcoin, Crypto Wallet & Trading
playstore_details.description:
The Coinhako app is used, downloaded and trusted by hundreds of thousands of retail traders in Asia for quick and easy access to cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin, Ethereum, Chainlink, Polkadot, XRP, Dai, Zilliqa, DeFi cryptocurrencies and much more.
 
Designed on the principles of ease-of-use, convenience, and security, we have been a top choice for users in Asia since 2014, and you will be able to enjoy the following features in countries like Singapore and Vietnam – and the rest of the APAC market subsequently – while on-the-go with the Coinhako app:
 
1. Bitcoin, Ethereum and cryptocurrency trading with fiat currencies – SGD, VND, USD 
2. Multi payment options to fund your account and trade cryptocurrencies on Coinhako
– Card payments (Visa and Mastercard credit and debit cards): Instant fiat to cryptocurrency trading with card payments
– Direct bank transfers: Quick wallet funding with fiat currencies – SGD, VND
– Stablecoin funding for USD: Deposit USDT and USDC to enjoy immediate conversions to fiat USD 
– Other third-party payment providers
4. Swap: Cryptocurrency to cryptocurrency trading – BTC:ETH, ETH:LINK, and much more
5. A secure wallet to store, send & receive Bitcoin, Ethereum and cryptocurrencies at Coinhako 
6. Real-time price monitoring
7. Cryptocurrency rewards user loyalty programme
8. 24 / 7 customer support to accommodate the ‘always-on’ cryptocurrency landscape
 
Supported cryptocurrencies - BTC, BCH, DOT, ETH, LINK, LTC, XRP, ZIL, DAI and much more!
 
At Coinhako, our mission is to provide the APAC market with easy access to digital assets like Bitcoin, Chainlink, Ethereum, Polkadot, Defi cryptocurrencies, and any other tokenized assets that will come. As such, we are working to further expand our services for the markets we serve.
 
Stay tuned to our spaces like:
1. Our Telegram group: Click.coinhako.com/TGOfficial
2. Our Blog: Click.coinhako.com/blog
3. Our Information Page: Click.coinhako.com/informationpage
 
If you require assistance, have any suggestions or want to learn more, please chat with us at Click.coinhako.com/coinhakosupport.
 
If you enjoy your experience with Coinhako, do drop us a review and feedback for us to further improve our services.
 
Thank you for your support and for making Coinhako your choice.
